# CURSOR-SKILLS - Prompts (Markdown)

Aligned with skill [.cursor/skills/community/prompts-markdown/SKILL.md](.cursor/skills/community/prompts-markdown/SKILL.md).

## Structure

- Objective, general instructions, classification (when applicable), actions/tools.
- .system/.user pairs for extraction and formatting when applicable.

## Recommended patterns

- **Base model:** keep a reference model for new prompts (e.g. modelo-guest.md).
- Naming: prompt-{name}-{context}.md or prompt-principal.md; V1/V2 versioning in subfolders.

## Best practices

- Clear language; output examples (JSON or text) when structured; reference tools/knowledge base when they exist.
